The paper discusses a communication method utilizing diffusion of carrier molecules, which falls under the category of information theory (cs.IT). The paper also proposes novel modulation schemes for molecular MIMO systems, which involves the use of nanomachines and can be considered a form of neural engineering (cs.NE) or systems and control (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper discusses the performance of these modulation schemes in terms of error rates, which can be considered a form of computational engineering (cs.CE) or multimedia (cs.MM).
